name:                raft
version:             0.1.0.0
synopsis:            Raft consensus protocol
description:         Please see README.md
homepage:            http://github.com/ahanikel/raft
license:             BSD3
license-file:        LICENSE
author:              Axel Hanikel
maintainer:          ahanikel@gmail.com
copyright:           2016 Axel Hanikel
category:            Distributed
